We would like a way to use our own tile provider rather than the OSM one. However, it appears that there is no way to provide our own via the public constructors in OpenStreetMapView.

A simple solution would be to add this constructor:

	public OpenStreetMapView(final Context context, final OpenStreetMapRendererInfo aRendererInfo, OpenStreetMapTileProvider provider)
	{
		this(context, null, aRendererInfo, provider);
	}

Could you please add this constructor to the code?
(unless there is some other way to do it already that I don't see)

Thanks!
